{"tid":2235909,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"主張一個中國 咁樣有有錯？","createTime":"2020-10-09T05:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T15:41:25.000Z","uid":2104,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3ce5922d180f96dbedacd729223c832ac2781d85","tid":2235909,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:20:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">一個中國</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\">中華民國</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n雖然台灣有聲音要擺脫中華民國<br />\n甚至唔承認中华人民共和国<br />\n但係台灣本島彭金馬地區確實係由一個叫中華民國嘅政府去管治<br />\n中華民國又好 台灣又好 將來係點都只有台灣人去決定<br />\n但係喺有改變之前<br />\n所謂中國有可能係描述緊中華民國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uYNPZ2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuYNPZ2W.jpg&h=e593e9a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nf5ufBh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNf5ufBh.jpg&h=5de64837&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m2Yr2gh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm2Yr2gh.jpg&h=592a9d07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ffb27304a6872024c2fda8bb44cc2876d96355d","tid":2235909,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:59:34.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d3b59b1a43037fdd2cc5b176a2cf2073f54807","tid":2235909,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:04:15.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"820b72099ac21b4ec4d867fd4b1a2389269918be","tid":2235909,"uid":7103,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:31:20.000Z","msg":"而家台灣人就係唔鳩想理中華民國個朵，因為一理就=九二共識個套，要同支那爭「中國」正統，兩岸統一<br />\n唔係話驚俾中國武統，而係覺得名義上，甚至武力上爭贏咗中國都唔知有乜利益，寧願自稱台灣，玩小國寡民，跟美國佬搵食<br />\n<br />\n但共產黨就最驚呢樣嘢，因為咁等於台灣人唔認自己係中國人，冇得行文化統戰條路，焗住武統（但根本冇實力）"},{"pid":"8a33c02d75ec717e123a8d5e864dfb9b0ff432ce","tid":2235909,"uid":7103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:33:40.000Z","msg":"承認中華民國=一個中國，即係中原嗰班係竊國賊<br />\n承認支那人民共和國=一個中國，即係台灣嗰班係分離主義者"},{"pid":"738306d6ca47311b14d72e9342192935a5574a47","tid":2235909,"uid":176958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"另一個大國，直頭極端恐怖組織啦<br />\n<br />\n生化襲擊，將責任歸咎於西方國家，極權統治，逆我者亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbce93db7b859eefcdd6bb56fbbb083a19febd1f","tid":2235909,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:41:00.000Z","msg":"劉備自稱漢，後人都叫番佢做蜀漢"},{"pid":"a6feda68d144d0aef799ba0fe28ec65699d62826","tid":2235909,"uid":293186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T07:57:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%259C%258B&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusryRJil42CLA7NmQUB0MJ4tY%3D&h=ac806f77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B</a>"},{"pid":"4d4ee1d76784e6cb43e61303e297bff0d2e2331f","tid":2235909,"uid":293186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:26:35.000Z","msg":"中華民國自成立後通稱或簡稱「中國」、「華」[39]。中華民國不承認中華人民共和國的合法性，而稱後者治下領土為大陸地區、大陸淪陷區"},{"pid":"ea39ce5c0598d2af84c92e017052b2eefd62fb81","tid":2235909,"uid":266010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:27:36.000Z","msg":"台灣就台灣 中國呢 就留返畀國民黨啦"},{"pid":"3376e1da79f7b7213f958df72bc92bd78eb2891e","tid":2235909,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:30:40.000Z","msg":"因為做中國人唔符合台灣人嘅政治經濟利益，所以台灣人應該將自己發明成島國以避免對大陸不必要嘅投入。放棄爭中國正統，就唔會拖入中國嘅戰爭，除非佢入侵。"},{"pid":"8885ce0273b6bc2802cd662cf05be0bff7146513","tid":2235909,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:41:38.000Z","msg":"邊個中國係聯合國入面咪邊個代表中國<br />\n中華民國要黎ff用"},{"pid":"42b622ac0aa500f240900f030a2b5653e1150284","tid":2235909,"uid":323720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"蔡總統快啲策劃返個北平事變，然後大陸五區易幟，拯救香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}